{
  "stem": "945.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they started retreat, then we started to see all three of them-- Romanians, Germans, and Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soldiers.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it, it-- towards the winter of '44, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] news really started coming more and more to the fact that the Russians were advancing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the same time, we were given to understand that when the Russians-- when the Germans or the Romanians retreat, they massacre the local Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So on the one hand, we were--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Romanians and the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jewish population--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whatever Jews were alive were in danger of being massacred.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't want to leave anybody alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, indeed, on the other side of the Bug, of course, that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They massacred all the Jewish people on the other side of the Bug.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the Romanian side, somehow the Romanians, as bad as they were, they were smart enough to realize that if the Germans lose they'll be faced with having to account for what they did.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the queen, the Romanian queen, and the influence she had from the-- from the local Jewish people that were in charge of the Jewish community-- a Dr.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Federer?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Filderman.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Filderman-- they impressed on the queen to somehow try and see that the Romanians don't commit the same atrocities as the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Romanians realized, too, that maybe the Germans were going to lose the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So things started to change.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that salt was an item which wasn't available.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Romania there were a lot of salt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for a wagon of salt you could barter for food and from a lot of stuff.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they sent salt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They sent money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They did what they could to help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it saved a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
